{
  "texts": [
    "Accordingly, MR systems involve adding environmentaware 2D/3D content into the real world.",
    "It can present a transition experience between VR and AR as virtual objects can be superimposed on the real-time dynamic real world.",
    "Object detection plays a crucial role in achieving the Metaverse and is widely used in XR.",
    "Face detection is a common task in VR, whereas text recognition is prevalent in AR.",
    "Advanced AR applications may require object recognition to link a 3D model to the physical world, which necessitates accurate object detection and class recognition algorithms."
  ]
}